texts.text: >Everybody is still in a panicked frenzy.
Good, good. Be the ones that slit your own throats.
>Suddenly, something grazes the man's cheek.
Nyarlathotep, found you!
Ah, so you can see me.
That's right. Honey sees right through your disguise.
That icky, black soul tells me who you really are!
Team Honey, get him!
>Honey's demons attack Nyarlathotep all at once.
>Nyarlathotep grimaces while deflecting their attacks.
Now I see. You are neither human nor demon.
You are a human creation. An android.
Ney, a Homunculus.
Honey's no ordinary Homunculus.
I'm a special Homunculus! Check this out!
This illusion is supposed to make humans appear as demons and vice versa.
But it seems that it has no effect on you.
Are you saying that you know the true identity of all these fools?
Yeah! Honey's a special Homunculus!
I can see what's inside, like spirits and stuff too!
There's no way your cheap tricks will work on me!
>Unbeknownst to its identity, cultists begin running to Nyarlathotep's side.

Hey, are you okay?!
We're coming to help!
Die, you monster!
Oh, Honey looks like a demon to them...!
Please, open your eyes!
What are you talking about? Take this!
Ow...! Please, listen! Honey's not a demon!
I'm not a human either but...
That means you're a monster either way!
Who cares?! That's not the point!
Honey's Honey! That's that!
Forget it! I just need to do something about Nyarlathotep!

*Snicker*
But can you find me...?

There you are!
What?!
>Just as Honey tries to attack Nyarlathotep,
>someone else lands an attack on her.
No! Who's trying to stop me...?!
Not even my demon can one shot it...
This demon's strong...!

Four eyes?!
It's me, Honey!
Now demons are calling me that...?
And how do you know Honey's name?!
Unless... You killed her...!
No! It's Honey, honest!
What are you talking about?! No, you're not fooling me!
You don't believe me?!
That's it! I'm telling Megakin!
Megakin! Megakin! It's Honey!
Honey?! Yo, the Hideout's been overrun by demons!
They got in through the Church of False Gods somehow!
Yo, I don't even know where Vagit and the others went either.
It's like they were all replaced by demons or somethin'!
Or maybe they got eaten...!
No, that's not what's going on! Some people just look like demons now!
Yo, they're demons every which way you look at them!
Wait, they ain't attakin' the Summonin' Portal...
When can you get back here?!
I ain't gonna be able to hold out much longer yo!
Ugh! He doesn't get it either!
Okay, it's time to find Vince...
There he is! Vince, I finally found you!
>Honey runs towards Vince's soul.
You learned my name? That's pretty smart of you.
What...?
>Vince bats Honey away before she gets a chance to talk.
Vince...?
>She's forgotten all pain and simply stares stunned at Vince.
So you ate Honey...?
No... I'm Honey... It's me...!
Whatever you say.
Now die!
*Snicker*
Huh?
It's Honey!
You're alive!
Honey? There you are!
My head felt like it was about to blow a gasket.
No! That Honey's a fake!
Yeah, I get now that you didn't eat Honey.
That's what I've been trying to say! Honey's...!
But you need to stop saying her name...
Honey, come here! We gotta kick this thing's ass!
But... Vince...
>Honey sinks to the floor in disbelief.
Hah. Lost the will to fight? Still, no mercy!

*Snicker*
Such a delicious tragedy.
Ah, I may yet witness more by going outside...
>The Honey standing behind Vince begins to morph.
>The girl quietly heads towards the surface.
Devil Download!
*Growl*
Eek!
Outta my way!
Gwah!

So that's how it is...
Devil Download!
*Wince*
Shit. Reinfocements.
Please... Stop...
>Honey tries to run as she dodges her friends' demons' attacks.

*Scream*
Monster!
Run! Ruuun!
Wait! Don't leave me!
No! Don't come any closer!
No... The same thing's happening out there...
>As chaos ensues, a girl walks and looks on in delight.
*Laugh*
Wonderful! I have not witnessed such a wonderful farce in quite some time!
How can you be so calm? Get out of here!
*Roar*
>The demon spouts blood and collapses.
>The girl wipes the blood off her clothes and smiles.
So delightful to see these foolish creatures devouring themselves.
Wait, that's Nyarlathotep! No one has any idea what's going on!
Fine...
It's time for Honey to stop crying and be a big girl!
